snippet.title: O, mei seiren - KEYLOCKER [Lyric video]
snippet.description:
In a silent world where music has been prohibited, B0B0 will serenade her rebellion against the vicious authorities by banding together with the Jukebot drummer, Rocket, to shatter the strings of fate and sing the melody of freedom in this unforgiving Rhythm Turn Based JRPG. 
Composition by: Elektrobear, for the soundtrack of Keylocker.
Voiced by: Psamathes.

Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/13...

Moonana Official Twitter: https://twitter.com/moonana_

Lyrics: Nana (Original lyrics in Saturnian, the language created for the universe of the game).

Henlaong, sillavoilla
Jot merla sarkassona
kikæ amaa kolapoilla
kolomitepet hekavoilla
voide koske holoren heona

[chorus]
seirent sa væ terja
O, mei seiren
seirent, O, mei seiren
mik verke len mejai
kyl mik mei æien
O, mei seiren
[end chorus]

volis ker væ heyl
villutolomit
mik meimer tak kel
kallev mei kikæ
kallev mik har væ sel

voide koske
nang len alta
nangik nangar
kyl mei kalla sa kohar
sahe meirke koske

jot ollutla sa len kyv len
voide koske, holoren heona

seirent sa væ terja, seirent
O, mei seiren
seirent, O, mei seiren
Sa mik ker voide, meimer hæk
kyl mik mei æien
O, mei seiren


Translation (English):

Fading hand reaching out, riveted
Pinned on the wall
Bruises all over
Folding pain up in his sleeve
Under current, sinking deep

[chorus]
Singing to the dead
O, I sing
singing, I sing
You’re one more number
For you I weep
O, I sing
[end chorus]

Sea Salt dripping from the sky
Healing pain in disguise
You were never mine
So why did I ache
When you fired the sign?

Sinking deep
Dont bring me up
Dont you dare
For I know to swim
But I chose to sink

Folding cranes to bring far near
Under current, sinking deep

Singing to the dead, singing
O, I sing
singing, I sing
For you to descend, my dear
For you I weep
O, I sing
